"hitting with my <i>Marksman</i> ability, and I deal 9 damage each for 4 "
"attacks. Use me to dislodge hard-to-hit units."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/02_Tutorial_part_2.cfg:963
